coll-book_creator_intro:
<big> nyi udi "wenza mikanda",udi bua kuenza mukanda udi nyi mabeji aa wiki adi wewa bua kusungula.
Udi bua kufila mukanda mushindu mishilashilangana(tshilejelu PDF anyi ODF) anyi kulomba dibeji dimana kuela.</big>
coll-book_creator_help: Kumona[[{{MediaWiki:Coll-helppage}}|dibeji dia diambuluisha bua mikanda]] bua malubu aa bunyi.
coll-book_creator_continue: Ku tunguluka ne dikuata mudimu nyi tshidi tshifuka mikanda
coll-book_creator_disable_text: "tshidi tshifuka mikanda" ne tshikala tshikanga ne mikanda udi ukuata nayi mudimu ne bayi kupula muaba udi ukuata mudimu.
